dct_title_s: Index to administrative units for Mito
dct_description_sm: Recto: Mito, Ibaraki-ken, Honshu, Japan. This index is for map on recto. It is filed under call number: G7964.M5C2.1946.A7M3. "Cauition this map for use only as administrative listing reference." "Administrative names and locations are correct to November 1943.
